    {
      "type": "articles",
      "specificArticles": [
        {
          "title": "",
          "textContent": "Casa Petri is situated in the historical center of Rosia Montana and is a heritage building where we preserved the traditional style like the wooden floor, the windows or the heating with terracotta stoves, but were we added modern facilities like the bathrooms. We have cosy spots around the house and a green yard with a nice view to the Cânic peak. It is not allowed to smoke inside or to listen loud music. <b>The booking will be confirmed by email.</b>"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "articles",
      "specificArticles": [
        {
          "title": "'Books' room",
          "textContent": "The downstairs room has one meter wide walls built out of rocks and a closet filled with books. It has private bathroom, two bunk beds and an expandable couch. <br><i class='fa fa-male'></i><i class='fa fa-male'></i> <i class='fa fa-arrows-h''></i> <i class='fa fa-male'></i><i class='fa fa-male'></i><i class='fa fa-male'></i><i class='fa fa-male'></i><i class='fa fa-male'></i><i class='fa fa-male'></i>",
          "images": [
            {
              "title": "'Books' room",
              "description": " here you can find ‘the cupboard with books’ - a cupboard transformed into a library where you can find old books and board games.",
              "thumbnailUrl": "img/accommodation/rooms/article/room1/thumbnail/1.jpg",
              "fullSizeUrl": "img/accommodation/rooms/article/room1/fullSize/1.jpg"
            },
            {
              "title": "'Books' room - inside",
              "description": " In the showcase are old photos from Roșia, crystal clusters rocks from the roman gallery and old objects used in the household.",
              "thumbnailUrl": "img/accommodation/rooms/article/room1/thumbnail/2.jpg",
              "fullSizeUrl": "img/accommodation/rooms/article/room1/fullSize/2.jpg"
            },
            {
              "title": "'Books' room - bathroom",
